                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h6>By click the Place Order button, you confirm that you have read and understood, and accept our Terms and Conditions, Return Policy, and Privacy Policy.</h6>
                    <div class="row justify-content-end" style="margin-right:2rem;">
                        <button class="btn btn-dark ">Place Order</button>
                    </div>
